'''额下沟'''（{{lang-en|Inferior frontal sulcus}}）是[[大脑|大脑]][[额叶|额叶]]的一条[[脑沟|脑沟]]，分隔了[[额中回|额中回]]和[[额下回|额下回]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Inferior Frontal Sulcus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/inferior-frontal-sulcus|accessdate=2021-04-09|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Inferior frontal sulcus|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/inferior-frontal-sulcus?lang=us|accessdate=2021-04-09|last=Gaillard|first=Frank|work=|publisher=Radiopaedia|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=额下沟|url=https://www.imaios.com/cn/e-Anatomy/node_322323/2731|accessdate=2021-04-09|work=IMAIOS|language=zh}}</ref>

== 功能 ==
一些[[神经成像|神经成像]]研究显示，额下沟可能与[[說謊|说谎]]、[[欺骗|欺骗]]有关，但尚无最终结论。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Contributions of Prefrontal Cortex and Executive Control to Deception: Evidence from Activation Likelihood Estimate Meta-analyses|url=https://doi.org/10.1093/cercor/bhn189|last=Christ|first=Shawn E.|last2=Van Essen|first2=David C.|date=2009-07-01|journal=Cerebral Cortex|issue=7|doi=10.1093/cercor/bhn189|volume=19|pages=1557–1566|issn=1047-3211|last3=Watson|first3=Jason M.|last4=Brubaker|first4=Lindsay E.|last5=McDermott|first5=Kathleen B.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Does the inferior frontal sulcus play a functional role in deception? A neuronavigated theta-burst transcranial magnetic stimulation study|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3474997/|last=Verschuere|first=Bruno|last2=Schuhmann|first2=Teresa|date=2012-10-18|journal=Frontiers in Human Neuroscience|doi=10.3389/fnhum.2012.00284|volume=6|issn=1662-5161|pmc=3474997|pmid=23087636|last3=Sack|first3=Alexander T.}}</ref>

